    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以Infra_RedisCache作为初始状态，idle是等待状态。那从idle到第一个处理状态是什么触发条件？是外部请求进来吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "idle"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
