      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，idle到parsing的转换已添加，标注DECODE和Infra_IngressController。接下来parsing之后应该到哪个状态？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "idle",
        "parsing"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "解析完成后自动进入extracting做函数提取，这里用AUTO触发，经过Load Balancer。然后extracting再自动到tracing做调用链追踪，还是走Ingress Controller。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "parsing",
