      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：parsing→extracting用AUTO，源是Infra_LoadBalancer；extracting→tracing也用AUTO，源是Infra_IngressController。然后tracing之后呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "parsing",
        "extracting",
        "tracing",
